26 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 24, Chapter 7, Subchapter 7, is amended
27 to add an additional section to read as follows:
28 24-7-739. Annuity payments owed to beneficiary of a special needs
29 trust.
30 (a) A member who designates a person or the parent or legal guardian
31 of a person who is designated as a beneficiary of an annuity or benefit under
32 § 24-7-706, § 24-7-709, § 24-7-711, or § 24-7-720 may elect to have the
33 annuity or benefit paid to a special needs trust that is established for the
34 benefit of the person under 42 U.S.C. § 1396p(d)(4)(A), as it existed on
35 January 1, 2025, or 42 U.S.C. § 1396p(d)(4)(C), as it existed on January 1,
36 2025.
